'''Unity'''是[[Canonical公司|Canonical公司]]为[[GNOME|GNOME]][[桌面环境|桌面环境]]所开发的[[图形用户界面|图形用户界面]]，用于[[Ubuntu|Ubuntu]][[操作系统|操作系统]]。Unity在Ubuntu 10.10[[Ubuntu_Netbook_Edition|上网本版]]中首次推出，最初是为了充分利用[[上网本|上网本]]有限的屏幕尺寸。<ref>{{cite web |last=Proffitt |first=Brian |title=Ubuntu Unity Interface Tailored for Netbook Screens |url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/196009/ubuntu_unity_interface_tailored_for_netbook_screens.html?tk=mod_rel |publisher=ITWorld |accessdate=28 October 2010 |date=2010-05-10 |archive-date=2010-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101031211310/http://www.pcworld.com/article/196009/ubuntu_unity_interface_tailored_for_netbook_screens.html?tk=mod_rel |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。不同於[[GNOME|GNOME]]、[[KDE_Software_Compilation|KDE SC]]，Unity并非一个桌面套件。

Unity是Aytana項目的一部分，而Aytana項目為提昇使用者對Ubuntu的體驗而設<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://wiki.ubuntu.com/Ayatana |title=Ayatana - Ubuntu Wiki |accessdate=2012-10-11 |archive-date=2012-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120517001045/https://wiki.ubuntu.com/Ayatana |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2017年4月，[[Mark_Shuttleworth|Mark Shuttleworth]]宣布將會在2018年轉回使用GNOME。 Ubuntu 17.04是最後一個預載 Unity 桌面環境的版本。[[Canonical公司|Canonical公司]]放棄原本桌面手機合一的路線，並將其重心轉移至[[雲端運算|雲端運算]]和[[物聯網|物聯網]]。<ref name="discontinued">{{cite web|url=https://insights.ubuntu.com/2017/04/05/growing-ubuntu-for-cloud-and-iot-rather-than-phone-and-convergence/|title=Growing Ubuntu for cloud and IoT, rather than phone and convergence|date=5 April 2017|first=Mark|last=Shuttleworth|work=[[Canonical_Ltd.|Canonical Ltd.]]|access-date=5 April 2017|archive-date=2017-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170507225729/https://insights.ubuntu.com/2017/04/05/growing-ubuntu-for-cloud-and-iot-rather-than-phone-and-convergence|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=Ubuntu-Dropping-Unity | title=Ubuntu To Abandon Unity 8, Switch Back To GNOME | publisher=[[Phoronix|Phoronix.com]] | access-date=2017-04-06 | archive-date=2017-05-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170516161705/http://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=Ubuntu-Dropping-Unity | dead-url=no }}</ref> {{tsl|fr|UBports|}}創始人Marius Gripsgård宣布將會接手Unity的開發。<ref name="Nestor07Apr17">{{cite web|url = http://news.softpedia.com/news/unity-8-now-has-a-new-home-over-at-ubports-development-will-start-very-soon-514663.shtml|title = Unity 8 Now Has a New Home Over at UBports, Development Will Start Very Soon|accessdate = 8 April 2017|last = Nestor|first = Marius|work = [[Softpedia|Softpedia]]|date = 7 April 2017|archive-date = 2020-06-20|archive-url = https://archive.today/20200620212522/https://news.softpedia.com/news/unity-8-now-has-a-new-home-over-at-ubports-development-will-start-very-soon-514663.shtml}}</ref> Unity 8現由UBports開發及發佈。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.github.com/ubports/unity8|title=ubports/unity8|accessdate=2018-05-18|work=GitHub|language=en|archive-date=2022-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220218201058/https://github.com/ubports/unity8}}</ref>

==使用者介面==
[[File:Ubuntu_13.04_Desktop.png|thumb]]

Unity介面包含了以下元素：
*上方工具列：一個多功能的工具列，有以下功能：（1）這是目前正在使用中的程式的選單工具列。（2）對於目前最大化的程式，在此有關閉、縮小和最小化的按鈕。（3）在右上角是系統選單，裡面包含系統設定、登出、關機等動作。（4）在系統選單左邊有時間、音量、電池狀態（筆電或平板電腦）、藍牙狀態、網路狀態、輸入法等資訊。
*啟動器：這算是一種[[Dock|Dock]]，這裡可以放置使用者常用的程式，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://help.ubuntu.com/12.04/ubuntu-help/shell-apps-favorites.html |title=改變要讓啟動器顯示什麼應用程式 |accessdate=2014-08-08 |work= |publisher=Ubuntu Documentation Team |date= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151215160213/https://help.ubuntu.com/12.04/ubuntu-help/shell-apps-favorites.html |archivedate=2015-12-15 }}</ref>只要點擊就會開啟開程式。電腦上的可卸除裝置和垃圾桶也顯示在此。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://help.ubuntu.com/12.04/ubuntu-help/unity-launcher-intro.html |title=使用啟動器啟動應用程式 |accessdate=2014-08-08 |work= |publisher=Ubuntu Documentation Team |date= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130526143109/https://help.ubuntu.com/12.04/ubuntu-help/unity-launcher-intro.html |archivedate=2013-05-26 }}</ref>啟動器也用來切換已經開啟的程式，已經開啟的程式在其圖案左側會有一個小小的白色箭頭。只要點擊已開啟程式的圖示就會切換到該程式。所有現在開啟的程式都會顯示在啟動器上。如果一個程式現在有多個視窗開啟，那箭頭的數量也會對應增加。滑鼠雙擊該圖示會顯示該程式所有已開啟視窗的縮圖。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://help.ubuntu.com/12.04/ubuntu-help/shell-windows-switching.html |title=在視窗間切換 |accessdate=2014-08-08 |work= |publisher=Ubuntu Documentation Team |date= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140811164743/https://help.ubuntu.com/12.04/ubuntu-help/shell-windows-switching.html |archivedate=2014-08-11 }}</ref>
*Dash：啟動器最上方的Ubuntu圖示可以用來開啟Dash，按下「Super」鍵（在多數電腦上是Windows鍵，在Mac電腦上是⌘鍵）也能開啟Dash。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://help.ubuntu.com/14.04/ubuntu-help/windows-key.html |title=什麼是「Super」鍵？ |accessdate=2014-08-08 |work= |publisher=Ubuntu Documentation Team |date= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140701041823/https://help.ubuntu.com/14.04/ubuntu-help/windows-key.html |archive-date=2014-07-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>Dash可以用來搜尋和瀏覽電腦上和網路上的程式、檔案、照片、音樂、影片、書籤等等。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://help.ubuntu.com/12.04/ubuntu-help/unity-dash-intro.html |title=用 Dash 尋找程式、檔案、音樂以及更多東西 |accessdate=2014-08-08 |work= |publisher=Ubuntu Documentation Team |date= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130526115516/https://help.ubuntu.com/12.04/ubuntu-help/unity-dash-intro.html |archivedate=2013-05-26 }}</ref>
*HUD（[[抬頭顯示器|抬頭顯示器]]）：可以用來搜尋程式的下拉選單。某些程式，如繪圖軟體[[GIMP|GIMP]]和辦公軟體[[LibreOffice|LibreOffice]]有數十個下拉選單項目。使用HUD可以讓使用者快速搜尋並使用他們想要的功能。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://help.ubuntu.com/12.04/ubuntu-help/unity-hud-intro.html |title=什麼是 HUD？ |accessdate=2014-08-08 |work= |publisher=Ubuntu Documentation Team |date= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151215160223/https://help.ubuntu.com/12.04/ubuntu-help/unity-hud-intro.html |archivedate=2015-12-15 }}</ref>'''

