=== Unity 2D ===
Canonical公司曾經維護兩種不同的Unity版本，這兩種版本在外觀上幾無二致，但在技術結構上有所不同。

Unity是[[Compiz|Compiz]]的一個插件，<ref name="CompizPlugin">{{cite web |url=http://askubuntu.com/questions/13073/is-unity-just-a-plugin-of-compiz |date=2010-11-13 |author=fluteflute |title=Is unity just a plugin of compiz |quote=The version of Unity that will be released in 11.04 is definitely implemented as plugin(s) in Compiz. |accessdate=2014-08-08 |archive-date=2011-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110707175308/http://askubuntu.com/questions/13073/is-unity-just-a-plugin-of-compiz |dead-url=no }}</ref>使用一個不常見的[[OpenGL|OpenGL]]工具套件Nux。<ref name=ars_technica_2013-10-17>{{cite web | url=http://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2013/10/ubuntu-13-10-review-the-linux-os-of-the-future-remains-a-year-away/ | title=Ubuntu 13.10 review: The Linux OS of the future remains a year away | website=Ars Technica | first=Ryan | last=Paul | date=17 October 2013 | accessdate=2 November 2013 | archive-date=2013-11-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103084435/http://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2013/10/ubuntu-13-10-review-the-linux-os-of-the-future-remains-a-year-away/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>因為Unity是Compiz的插件，因此在相容的系統上可以使用[[圖形處理器|圖形處理器]]加速提升效能。Unity以[[C++|C++]]和[[Vala|Vala]]程式語言寫成。

Unity 2D是一系列獨立的程式，<ref name="2D-Components">[[:File:Unity-2D_Natty.png|:File:Unity-2D Natty.png]]</ref>開發給Compiz無法運行的環境使用，例如顯示卡不支援OpenGL的環境。Unity 2D以[[Qt|Qt]]架構的GUI建構語言[[QML|QML]]寫成<ref name="2D-QML">{{cite web|url=http://developer.qt.nokia.com/forums/viewthread/3214/|title=Canonical building Unity 2D on QML and Qt | Qt DevNet forums | Qt Developer Network|accessdate=2014-08-08|archive-date=2011-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110314195132/http://developer.qt.nokia.com/forums/viewthread/3214/|dead-url=no}}</ref>預設下使用[[Metacity|Metacity]]視窗管理員，<ref name="2D-Components" />但也可以使用Compiz或[[KWin|KWin]]之類的加速視窗管理員。自Ubuntu 11.10開始，Unity 2D取代了傳統GNOME面板，成為硬體無法執行Compiz版Unity的情況下的備用方案。<ref name="OMG27May11">{{Cite news|url = http://www.omgubuntu.co.uk/2011/05/unity-2d-lands-in-oneiric-daily-build|title = Unity 2D lands in Oneiric daily build|accessdate = 27 May 2011|last = Sneddon|first = Joey|authorlink = |date = May 2011|work = OMG Ubuntu!|archive-date = 2018-07-12|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180712221240/https://www.omgubuntu.co.uk/2011/05/unity-2d-lands-in-oneiric-daily-build}}</ref>

Unity 2D自從2012年10月的Ubuntu 12.10之後就不再被維護了，因為3D版已經可以在更低階的硬體上執行。<ref name="omgubuntu1">{{cite web |url=http://www.omgubuntu.co.uk/2012/05/uds-q-summary-bye-bye-unity-2d-hello-gnome-shell-spin |title=UDS-Q Summary: Bye-Bye Unity 2D, Hello GNOME-Shell Spin |publisher=Omgubuntu.co.uk |date=2012-05-12 |accessdate=2012-07-07 |archive-date=2021-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210618201440/https://www.omgubuntu.co.uk/2012/05/uds-q-summary-bye-bye-unity-2d-hello-gnome-shell-spin }}</ref>

== 提供Unity的发行版 ==
Unity主要是为[[Ubuntu|Ubuntu]]开发的，因此Ubuntu中提供了最新的 Unity。

除了Ubuntu，其他[[Linux发行版|Linux发行版]]也尝试引入Unity。
* [[Arch_Linux|Arch Linux]]通过Unity-for-Arch项目提供了Unity,<ref>{{cite web | url = https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Unity_(%E7%AE%80%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87) | publisher = Arch Linux Wiki | title = Unity | accessdate = 2016-12-17 | archive-date = 2019-12-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191220040044/https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Unity_(%E7%AE%80%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87) }}</ref> 但是安装它意味着需要将大量的软件包替换成Ubuntu的版本。
* [[Fedora_Linux|Fedora Linux]]开发者宣布有意把Unity导入Fedora，但这项计划被推迟到 Fedora 15，且現已因無進展而取消。<ref name="fedora_unity">{{cite web | url=https://www.pcworld.com/businesscenter/article/220085/fedora_and_opensuse_linux_drop_unity_efforts.html | title=Fedora and openSUSE Linux drop Unity efforts | publisher=PC World | accessdate=2011-12-20 | author=Noyes, Katherine | archive-date=2012-01-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120118173255/http://www.pcworld.com/businesscenter/article/220085/fedora_and_opensuse_linux_drop_unity_efforts.html }}</ref>

